in number of\natoms in the system. The method is not tied to a particular wave-function\nrepresentation, making it suitable for inclusion in any AIMD software package.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Dec 2008 17:03:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 7 Feb 2009 17:49:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Apr 2009 09:39:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-21"}
